title: [Empath Guild, Broom Closet]
description: Thin shafts of sunlight trickle in through the open door of the closet to illuminate a series of bamboo shelves lined with cleaning supplies.   A large dust bin sits cater-cornered near several brooms and mops resting inside a large steel bucket.
